###7. Scope limits
We are modeling Probability of Default (PD) only; we will not estimate Loss Given Default (LGD).
We will strictly drop post-approval behavioral variables (e.g., recoveries, total_rec_prncp, last_pymnt_amnt) to prevent data leakage. We are building an origination/application scorecard.

###8. Risks and fallback
Risk: SHAP values from the LightGBM model exhibit wild non-linearities that cannot be smoothed into a monotonic, compliant scorecard format. Fallback: Enforce monotonic constraints natively inside the LightGBM hyperparameters (monotone_constraints), forcing the algorithm to only learn regulatory-compliant trees before extracting SHAP values.

